title: ‘Stranger Things’: The Duffer Brothers on Vol. 2’s Major Reveals and What to Expect From Series Finale: “We’re Not Trying to Shock or Upset Anyone”
summary: "I hope by the time people get to the end that it feels like there’s something inevitable about what happens," Matt Duffer tells The Hollywood Reporter in a conversation with brother Ross Duffer about the payoff moments in the final season, and how it all leads into their endgame.
